{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ba278b2b2c","title":"陈伯达戚本禹接见人民日报社工作人员的谈话摘要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bdee81694d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":7,"articleId":"ba278b2b2c","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"新闻广播和出版","id":"268718f23b","type":"主题"},{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"戚本禹","id":"57434e107b","type":"人物"},{"name":"聂元梓","id":"8e7eaace26","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"},{"id":"9014e20fdf","name":"戚本禹"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"07df91f88e","type":"title","text":"陈伯达戚本禹接见人民日报社工作人员的谈话摘要","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ba278b2b2c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6e345b1f0e","type":"paragraph","text":"10月7日，陈伯达、戚本禹同志接见人民日报社论组，接见中途，在人民日报工作的一些学生走进来，伯达同志问了他们是哪个学校，回答是清华、北大、北航的。在他们回答时，伯达说：“向清华致敬！”“向北大致敬！”“向北航致敬！”","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ba278b2b2c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"75ebbb9868","type":"paragraph","text":"清华：我们两派联合起来了。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ba278b2b2c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"47e86d5b82","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：我不相信，要真联合，不要假联合。周家缨贴我的大字报，我是保护他的。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ba278b2b2c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"04a76bf6ca","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你刚才还不是说原则的政策是唯一正确的政策吗？","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ba278b2b2c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"72ba7b96a0","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：我是有原则的，他能贴我的大字报，上纲那么高，这就说明他不简单哪！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ba278b2b2c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8e540265bf","type":"paragraph","text":"北大蒋××：我们两派还没有联合起来。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ba278b2b2c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"842392c46b","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：北大的两派联合是困难的，我那次讲话要北大取消动态组，保卫组，航空版，这是新北大的心头肉。但是北大井冈山，也干得太厉害了，我话还没讲完，就去抄保卫组，要抄也要先给人家打个招呼，让人家做个准备嘛！人家说我是保聂派。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ba278b2b2c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92895cac1b","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：新北大公社是个很好的组织。革命性是很强的。他们保聂元梓不是保聂元梓的错误，保的是第一张马列主义大字报。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ba278b2b2c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"150b2ee9f2","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：我们都保嘛！……我现在也不同意周培源当校长了。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ba278b2b2c","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}